# Shaping the future with java faster

  - Java 10 release
   - Tools
    - Java mission control - More tracing functionlaity -  https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/troubleshoot/tooldescr002.html
    - Java flight recorder- Agent for storing profiling data: https://docs.oracle.com/javacomponents/jmc-5-4/jfr-runtime-guide/about.htm#JFRUH170
    - Application Class Data SHaring - Shared data across different apps- https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/vm/class-data-sharing.html
   - Type inference
   - Garbage Collection- 
     - ZGC
       - GC Pause times not exceeding 10ms
